name: Old School Swimsuit
description:
Greetings

This is a Lora model trained on old school swimsuit.

This Lora was trained based on NAI. It should work with a variety of models.

What you can do with it:

・An old school swimsuit appears.

・If you enter "nipple" in the prompt, it will take off the swimsuit relatively correctly.

Experimental:

・Support for a little nsfw.(Putting "nsfw" in the effect of the prompt helps a bit.)

・Putting "cum" in the prompt also works.(I included a few teacher images)

IMPORTANT !

  1. Strength of 0.6~0.7 is good.

  2. If you do not want the name tag to appear, enter "name_tag" in the negative prompt.

  3. If you want to include a name tag, enter "name_tag" in the prompt.

  4. The trigger prompt is "one-piece swimsuit", but adding "old school swimsuit" along with it might have a good effect.IDK.

If you really like it, please consider a small donation.

The donated money will be used to pay for electricity.
